NOTES
=====


HTML
----
Uses skeleton ( http://getskeleton.com/ ) for the base layout.

Virtualenv
----------
Included for ease


Apache config
-------------
Add this to the apache config:

        AddHandler cgi-script .cgi
        AddHandler wsgi-script .wsgi
        Alias /static/ </path/to/weru/archivist>/static/
        <Directory "</path/to/weru/archivist>/static">
                Order allow,deny
                Options Indexes
                Allow from all
                IndexOptions FancyIndexing
        </Directory>
        WSGIScriptAlias / </path/to/weru>/django.wsgi


